'''托尼斯普里'''（{{lang-ka|თონის პური}}）是一種[[喬治亞|喬治亞]][[麵包|麵包]]食物。和普通麵包不同的是，托尼斯普里經過炭火直接烘烤而成。托尼斯普里主要在[[復活節|復活節]]、[[聖誕節|聖誕節]]和[[新年|新年]]，以及生日和婚禮等慶典時食用<ref>{{cite news |title=MARKETS Georgia on My Mind |url=http://pqasb.pqarchiver.com/latimes/access/60313622.html?dids=60313622:60313622&FMT=ABS&FMTS=ABS:FT&date=Jun+03%2C+1993&author=LINDA+BURUM&pub=Los+Angeles+Times+(pre-1997+Fulltext)&desc=MARKETS+Georgia+on+My+Mind&pqatl=google |work=[[Los_Angeles_Times|Los Angeles Times]] |date=1993-06-03 |accessdate=2008-04-02 |first=Linda |last=Burum |archive-date=2012-11-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121104185639/http://pqasb.pqarchiver.com/latimes/access/60313622.html?dids=60313622:60313622&FMT=ABS&FMTS=ABS:FT&date=Jun+03,+1993&author=LINDA+BURUM&pub=Los+Angeles+Times+(pre-1997+Fulltext)&desc=MARKETS+Georgia+on+My+Mind&pqatl=google |dead-url=no }}</ref>。
